Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}聖天空戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要墜入愛河每個人都會變得如此孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正擁抱著比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切必定都是為了讓我倆能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用淚水來呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你早就給了我 最寶貴的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是我的幻覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.09,0:01:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是阿斯多利亞王國的邊陲地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裏的森林遇見了光之天使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字叫亞連·歇薩爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當他的巨人打贏了艾斯嘉科尼時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了不祥的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她又…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳，你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連，你快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快帶著大家逃離這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不見的敵人會來攻擊這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來人型裝甲的戰鬥\N給你帶來了太大的刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的會燒起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切都會被火焰包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔性的美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊法尼利亞的那個看不見的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將一切都給燒燬了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在胡說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女孩怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩聽說是從幻之月來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說幻之月會招來災禍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:02:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這座城會發生什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住□
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亞的士兵不準被迷信沖昏了頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為我部下的無禮向你致歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是累了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回房休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？德歐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在森林裏抓到一個可疑的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑的傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成那女孩所說的話是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大，我把她帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:03:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們認識嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是法尼利亞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於見到您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露，法尼利亞的情況怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都…全都燒掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城裏的武士們全都死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存活下來的人也離散到各地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有半個人在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在找
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好你還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會燒起來？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她發高燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵，把那女孩也一起帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍就快消失不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的理想未來已經開始出現動搖了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是讓龍就這樣逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將無法預測這會為我們的未來產生多少影響
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把龍抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:05:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道龍在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亞是同盟國
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是慢慢等外交交涉那獵物早就溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必要這樣把事情鬧大？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要穿上你製作的隱形披風
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不會韶下是我們寨巴哈帝國所為的證據啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好期待戰利品吧，軍師大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不放心讓那些士兵\N來照顧你們這兩位女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她一定很擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的母親一定是個美人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家母在我小時候就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的，那是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.94,0:07:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，家母的確是個美人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是個喜愛花朵的溫柔女性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從某天家妹無故失蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家母就因為傷心過度而臥病在床
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果家妹還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該差不多跟你一樣大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不曉得該怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一談起家人，我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明才跟天野學長告白沒多久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣是不是真的很隨便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這粒種子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去下馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到城裏去巡視一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…請你小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人真的已經來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麼事情，我都會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是國王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑到這種地下牢房來\N是來妨礙我睡午覺的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你這種森林居民身上\N應該帶有格拉爾的葉子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會知道這種葉子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我王兄告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說它可以中和大部分的毒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地鼠，幫我扶著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有夠大牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到連隊長都跟著迷信起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在的非常戒備狀態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意那個幻之月女孩所說的話，對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在意的是那個迪蘭度的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的眼睛散發出渴望鮮血的瘋狂兇光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道寨巴哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會對我們發動攻擊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會停靠在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表示他們知道艾斯嘉科尼就在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦發動攻擊他們一定會趕盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的會這麼狠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們就會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不韶活□也就不會韶下證據
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把庫魯傑特準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧，裏殿\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候要動手，迪蘭度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機繼續待命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不陪你們玩捉迷藏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是幻之月來的女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻貓正往我這邊看著…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的短髮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服也很怪異
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都像隻貓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那對耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那條尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她的個性能再溫馴一點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是我睡在長椅上？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像在生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有東西正往這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑到哪裏去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把病人放著不管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您為了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是為了做那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你要幹嘛啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:13:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜靜的別亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草的毒素經由傷□跑了進去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能退燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不見的巨人來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是看不見的巨人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是幻之月招來的噩運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，是寨巴哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要以謝拉撒特迎敵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼！手無縛雞之力的人們！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人！打開缺口了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！突入！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一切都破壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用煙把艾斯嘉科尼給逼出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的寨巴哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇歐，你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大，我真是丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人在什麼地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是從地下通道入侵進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經抵擋不住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經搬上庫魯傑特了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫魯傑特？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座城已經失守
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候撒退了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要逃？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有…已經有這麼多夥伴犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能再讓更多人犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣還算是武士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會背對著敵人逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了替法尼利亞的人民報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會戰到至死方休
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇死亡的匹夫之勇並不是真正的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵，你是法尼利亞王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要王在，人民在，希望也就在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍住這份屈辱才是真正的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士的生命是為了讓人們活下去而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點你不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇歐，將司令部移至庫魯傑特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳令下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會將你，還有艾斯嘉科尼交給寨巴哈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以亞連·歇薩爾之名發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差這個閥門了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個鐘乳洞不會受到影響
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備完畢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人在哪裏？他不在這裏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們馬上就會過來會合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收錨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收錨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出航
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒吧，燒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.19,0:17:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢至極
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到何時才要停止這種無謂的殺戮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最確實消滅證據的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來只要將被我熏出來的艾斯嘉科尼逮住就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂的阿斯多利亞的亞連\N會因為遭到火攻就乖乖就範嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟想說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城的後方有處斷崖瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.01,0:18:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說有烏在瀑布之中築巢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了躲避敵人的攻擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙在城的後方！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，揚帆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揚帆！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊境的烏合之眾還挺有本事的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你們打下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在漂浮的狀態下是無法使用隱形披風的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把看見的人全部解決就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要去哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亞的都城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算浮游要塞也追不上這艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人型裝甲竟然會飛？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:19:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:19:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上方被制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再讓你們這些混帳為所欲為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身手不錯，迪蘭度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很強嘛，亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓我開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連，上面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭到攻擊，舵不受控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為艾斯嘉科尼使得大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士的生命是為了讓人們活下去而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵，你打算做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼變成了飛龍？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛龍？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來那就是多倫卡喀大人所說的龍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪，這裏交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別走，迪蘭度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，追過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人要離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是為了讓我們逃走，才…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你千萬不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.44,0:22:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪斯，請把船調頭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去救梵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.67,0:22:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒辦法馬上調頭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帆被弄壞了，舵也不受控制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.12,0:22:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.96,0:22:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.96,0:22:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之風就快來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.80,0:22:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好，乘上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.21,0:22:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好久沒獵龍了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.81,0:22:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我來好好玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.19,0:24:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我早該宰了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.86,0:24:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快，我得快去通知他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.17,0:24:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.30,0:24:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟的刻印
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:14.16,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月兒彼方藍色探照燈照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:22.61,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降臨的天使 你究竟是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.07,0:23:30.24,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的門扉即將開啟　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:36.39,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放過這令人興奮的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:38.75,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:43.76,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃燒般的神秘雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.83,0:23:47.60,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真無邪的笑容讓我傾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.67,0:23:51.40,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深處的暗示只傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.47,0:23:55.41,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了無止盡的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.47,0:23:58.91,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心的鼓動無法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.97,0:24:06.38,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想帶著你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:14.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:22.60,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.07,0:23:30.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:36.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:38.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:43.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.83,0:23:47.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.66,0:23:51.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.47,0:23:55.40,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.47,0:23:58.91,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.97,0:24:06.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい

